  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为在线学习平台画一个上下文图，核心是这个叫EstudaOnlinePlatform的系统，主要面向三类用户：管理员、教师和学生。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sistemaEAD",
        "administrador",
        "professor",
        "aluno"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，三类用户都是人形角色对吧？管理员这边是普通的系统管理员还是学校层面的管理者？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "administrador"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是学校的管理层，比如校长或教务主任，所以标注成\"Administrador/Diretor\"更准确，他们负责整个平台的运营管控。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "administrador"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把管理员角色加上去了。那教师和学生的职责边界需要我特别注意吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "professor",
        "aluno"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "教师负责发布课程内容，学生则是消费端，观看课程。我想把平台本身框在一个容器边界里，强调这是一个封闭的系统环境。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "professor",
        "aluno",
        "sistema",
        "sistemaEAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "容器边界命名为\"plataforma\"，里面放置EstudaOnlinePlatform系统，描述写成\"Onde os usuários podem acessar as aulas e seus dados\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sistema",
        "sistemaEAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，这样突出了平台的核心价值——访问课程和数据。现在来画关系线吧，管理员和平台之间是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "administrador",
        "sistemaEAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我理解为管理关系，标签用\"Administra\"，表示管理员对平台有完全的管理权限。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "administrador",
        "sistemaEAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "准确。教师那边是\"Publica aulas\"，强调内容生产者的角色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "professor",
        "sistemaEAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加教师到平台的关系。学生这边我初步想标注\"Acessa\"，但感觉不够具体？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "aluno",
        "sistemaEAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "\"Acessa\"太泛了，改成\"Assiste as aulas\"吧，直接点明学生的核心行为是上课，而不是管理或发布。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "aluno",
        "sistemaEAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "修改完成，学生关系现在标注为\"Assiste as aulas\"。标题我打算用\"Diagrama de contexto plataforma de EAD\"，符合葡萄牙语的语境。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "标题没问题。让我整体看一下：三个角色都指向平台容器，关系分别是管理、发布、观看，逻辑很清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "administrador",
        "professor",
        "aluno",
        "sistemaEAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "有个细节想确认：容器边界\"plataforma\"和系统\"EstudaOnlinePlatform\"的命名会不会让读者困惑？前者是抽象概念，后者是具体产品名。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sistema",
        "sistemaEAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这是有意为之的——\"plataforma\"代表业务层面的平台概念，EstudaOnlinePlatform是技术实现，这样技术人员和业务人员都能看懂。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sistema",
        "sistemaEAD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，这种分层表达确实有助于跨团队沟通。所有元素和关系都已就位，我最终检查一遍。",
      "elements_involved": [
